<meta content="The funding services are intended for mid-cap companies and SMEs (oy, oyj, ay, ky, osk) with 6-250 employees who operate in Finland and whose business is negatively affected by the coronavirus crisis. The funding will help businesses develop new products and working methods, but cannot be used to compensate for lost sales. Two forms of funding are available: preliminary and development funding. Businesses may not apply for both forms of funding simultaneously." name="description" property="description" />
